priorBusinessDay
the function takes a date as input, subtracts one day from it, and then iteratively subtracts days until it finds the last business day (excluding Sundays and Saturdays). Date is returned at the end

nextBusinessDay
 the function takes a date as input, adds one day to it, and then iteratively adds days until it finds the next business day (excluding Sundays and Saturdays).

reporting 
sub function combines data from different workbooks, sorts it, processes it, and generates a report and updates values in specific cells
